%E1%BA%A1n-L%C3%BD/S%C3%A1p-%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-ca/poem-aRKGLIS3fXEdf4EiJ2Kk3A">Sáp ương ca - 插秧歌</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/D%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-V%E1%BA%A1n-L%C3%BD/author-JSRpfYAHfq-c4bVKwnYGVg">Dương Vạn Lý</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%E1%BA%A7n-Qu%E1%BB%91c-To%E1%BA%A1i/Th%E1%BA%AFng-phong-h%E1%BA%A7u/poem-d3cBWrI5zb6nUZEcIClXmw">Thắng phong hầu - 勝封侯</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%E1%BA%A7n-Qu%E1%BB%91c-To%E1%BA%A1i/author-AiimLJIm9mZUvCnDU509wQ">Trần Quốc Toại</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%A2m-B%C3%B4/Ti%E1%BB%83u-chu/poem-U5ro2DHTHCi6DAS2FwvxLA">Tiểu chu - 小舟</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%A2m-B%C3%B4/author-LbaVSB66mX6k1U09t5TO2A">Lâm Bô</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Phan-Th%C3%BAc-Tr%E1%BB%B1c/Tr%C3%B9ng-ng%E1%BB%8D-nh%E1%BA%ADt-ph%E1%BA%A7n-ho%C3%A1-vong-th%C3%AA-c%C3%A2n-l%E1%BA%A1p-y-ph%E1%BB%A5c-t%E1%BA%A1i-m%E1%BB%99-c%E1%BA%A3m-t%C3%A1c/poem-RKbYHfnWSmPLFq5jsoPgSw">Trùng ngọ nhật phần hoá vong thê cân lạp y phục tại mộ cảm tác - 重午日棼化亡妻巾笠衣服在墓感作</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Phan-Th%C3%BAc-Tr%E1%BB%B1c/author-0CTnEDQGEKViETWZXrhgww">Phan Thúc Trực</a>)<br></div>	</div>
